課程教材 Course Material
	    Lyapunov theory is covered in many texts on linear systems, e.g., Linear Systems, Antsaklis & Michel, McGraw-Hill.
LQR and Kalman filtering are covered in many books on linear systems, optimal control, and optimization. One good one is Dynamic Programming and Optimal Control, vol. 1, Bertsekas, Athena Scientific. Another two are Optimal Filtering and Optimal Control: Linear Quadratic Methods, both Anderson & Moore, Dover.
     

參考書目 References
	    Nonlinear Lyapunov theory is covered in most texts on nonlinear system analysis, e.g., Nonlinear systems: Analysis, Stability, and Control, Sastry, Springer, or Nonlinear Systems Analysis (2nd edition), Vidyasagar, SIAM.    

