課程概述 Course Description
       將最小二次解用於線性態系統的控制及狀態估測問題上並進一步討論動態系統最佳化設計之各種非封閉解。

A continuation of “Linear Dynamical System (1)”. Optimal control and dynamic programming; linear quadratic regulator. Lyapunov theory and methods. Time-varying and periodic systems. Realization theory. Linear estimation and the Kalman filter. Examples and applications from digital filters, circuits, signal processing, and control systems.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    將最小二次解用於線性態系統的控制及狀態估測問題上並進一步討論動態系統最佳化設計之各種非封閉解
A continuation of “Linear Dynamical System (1)”. Optimal control and dynamic programming; linear quadratic regulator. Lyapunov theory and methods. Time-varying and periodic systems. Realization theory. Linear estimation and the Kalman filter. Examples and applications from digital filters, circuits, signal processing, and control systems.
     

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Linear quadratic regulator: Discrete-time finite horizon2LQR via Lagrange multipliers3Infinite horizon linear quadratic regulator4Continuous time linear quadratic regulator5Linear Quadratic Stochastic Control6Invariant subspaces7Estimation8The Kalman filter9Approximate nonlinear filtering10Linear Quadratic Stochastic Control with Partial State Observation11Invariant sets, conservation, and dissipation12Basic Lyapunov theory13Linear quadratic Lyapunov theory14Lyapunov theory with inputs and outputs15Linear matrix inequalities and the S-procedure16Analysis of systems with sector nonlinearities17Perron-Frobenius Theory18期末考 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


