                  高等線性系統                   

                     3學分3小時
                  





課程名稱
                    高等線性系統                 
 英文課程名稱
                    Advanced Linear Systems                 
 中文課程概要
                    本課程為線性系統之進階課程, 主要為碩士班以上之學生而設計。本課程之主要目的在對多輸入多輸出(MIMO)系統做深入之探討，內容包括MIMO系統之描述、特性分析及控制器設計。 

 英文課程概要
                    This is an advanced course to linear system theory, and is designed mainly for graduate students. The objective of this course is to let one have an extensive study to the behaviors of multivariable systems. In this course, we will introduce various methods of describing MIMO linear systems as well as ways of analyzing some of their properties. Controller design procedures are also introduced in the course. 







